results.title: Vive la Fantastique!
results.description: In Paris, Yvette Diamonde protests construction over a historic site; several people are transformed into ancient beings called the Ruined; the FF sets things right; Yvette finds that she has permanently acquired new powers -- just like the FF once did.

results.title: Reed Richards: Alone!
results.description: Reed's mind is clearly not up to par, but his fighting skills and his passion are well above normal; Johnny gets to know Caledonia better; the Press Gang (from Genosha) attacks Reed, and with the Trapster's help succeeds in capturing him.

results.title: The First -- The Final? -- Fire!
results.description: Sue, Ben, and Johnny investigate Reed's disappearance; they follow him to Genosha, where thet are attacked by Ayesha, captured by Crucible, and body-switched with other people; Johnny's body-switcher ignites his nova flame, which destroys the citadel.

results.title: Once More, O Green & Pleasant Land
results.description: Sue, Ben, and Johnny reunite with Reed and join forces with C. M. Anderson against Crucible and the Enclave; Sue, Ben, and Johnny get their rightful bodies back; Reed confronts Crucible and gets his genius back; the FF evict Crucible and co. from Genosha.

results.title: I, Ronan
results.description: The FF, Franklin, and Caledonia all dream that Ronan killed the FF; atop Four Freedoms Plaza, federal authorities prepare to return three Kree prisoners home; Ronan attacks and transports the FF, the Kree, Detective Jones, and even the Plaza to the moon.

results.title: The Moon is a Lonely Place to Die Hard!
results.description: The FF fight Ronan on the moon; Ronan infects Sue with a Mannequin, which binds her to his will; Reed, Ben, and Johnny defeat the three Kree warriors; Ronan and Sue head for the home of the Watcher; meanwhile, Bounty is hired to retrieve Caledonia.

results.title: A Clash of Iron
results.description: SHIELD monitors the battle on the moon and calls Iron Man to help; his armor malfunctions and he battles Reed, Ben, and Johnny; Reed, Ben, and Johnny catch a glimpse of a future in which they died, Sue married Dr. Doom, and they had a daughter, Valeria.

results.title: Unnatural Selection
results.description: Margali Szardos transports the unknowing FF into a future where Dr. Doom joined the FF and Sue married him, and where the Kree and Brood have enslaved the earth; the FF battle the Kree Avengers and team up with Lucas and Redwing to defeat the Brood.
